name: PrimeRate

skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: prime rate
des: The prime rate is an important index used by banks to set rates on many consumer loan products, such as credit cards or auto loans. This skill gets the most recently published prime rate reported by The Wall Street Journal.
